{
  "texts": [
    "It contains 223 semantic triple groups, each paired with outputs from 8 triple-to-text generation systems.",
    "These texts were evaluated for fluency (FLU), grammar (GRA) and semantic equivalence (SEM).",
    "We investigate two families of open-source instruction-tuned LLMs.",
    "The first system is FlanT5 (Chung et al., 2022), T5 (Raffel et al., 2020) that have been instruction tuned on a diverse set of 1000 NLP tasks (Wang et al., 2022).",
    "The second system is Llama2-chat (Touvron et al., 2023), which is Llama2 tuned on instruction datasets."
  ]
}